cs.CL, cs.MM, cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.SI

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper proposes a novel end-to-end model for generating human-like live comments by referring to the video and other users' comments. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is also likely as the paper deals with live comments on videos. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is another possible category as the proposed model uses surrounding frames of the video to generate live comments. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is a possible category as the paper deals with generating relevant comments based on the video content. 
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is another possible category as the paper deals with generating interactive comments that are relevant to other users' comments.
